ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule I.1 to the Financial Administration Act
PrecisOrder amending Schedule I.1 to the FIINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT by striking out the reference to the Minister of Industry in column II of that Schedule opposite the name of Federal Economic Development Agency for Southern Ontario in column I of that Schedule and by substituting for that reference a reference to the Minister of Economic Development and Official Languages, effective November 20, 2019.
